cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.CV, cs.GR 

This paper involves the use of artificial intelligence and machine learning algorithms to improve the performance of an agent playing a video game. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.AI. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves game theory and decision making, which falls under the category of cs.GT (Game Theory). The paper also mentions the use of computer vision techniques to analyze game states, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper involves the use of search algorithms, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics).
